<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70;">  2.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> 老师是</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold;">**只读咨询台**</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">：不要把笔记、代码、实验结果回灌进 notebook。</span></span>
